caption:
🔧We're holding a bonus new volunteer orientation on September 25th at 6 pm. Come learn the ins and outs of volunteering in the shop. The orientation takes about 20 mins and is mandatory if you want to get involved. No RSVP required!

🔨No bike experience? No problem! Volunteering is a great way to learn, we love beginners, and there are other ways to get involved.

🐌Can't make it? We hold an orientation on the first Wednesday of every month, so join us Oct 2nd.

🙌Can’t wait for our cleanup on Saturday Sept 21 at Coronation Park for the @UofTTrashTeam Urban Litter
Challenge! Join us on our group ride to help prevent litter in our watershed from entering Lake Ontario. Every piece
counts, so register to lend a hand.
9:15am: Meet at Bikechain
9:30am: Roll out to Coronation Park
10:15am: Start Clean-up
11:30am: Wrap up 
We'll have the option to bike back together after the clean up too.
